ls). Uses Option[Plugin[Authorizer]] and delegates to the authorizer plugin for ACL operations.\n\n8. KafkaApisBuilder.java (kafka.server.builders.KafkaApisBuilder) - A builder class for constructing KafkaApis instances with dependency injection. Contains a field for Optional<Plugin<Authorizer>> authorizerPlugin that is used during object construction."
